BATTERY 4 is the cutting-edge drum sampler designed for the 21st century. It combines a supercharged library, tailor-made for electronic and hip hop music, with a radically-intuitive workflow that keeps the focus on creativity. Instantly find and arrange sounds with a new, tag-based browser, and route powerful new effects with drag-and-drop simplicity. With a clear, compelling interface that puts incredible power at your fingertips, BATTERY 4 launches drum sampling into the future.

Version 4.1.0
- Added support for Avid Audio eXtension (AAX Native 64 bit).
- Advanced integration in MASCHINE 2.0 host software.
- Insert Effect Power Buttons now automatable.
- Fixed problems with Output configuration recall in certain situations.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install Battery 4 v4.1.0

Dellete .plist

Macintosh HD /Library/Preferences/com.native-instruments.Battery 4.plist
Macintosh HD /Users/you_name/Library/Preferences/com.native-instruments.Battery 4.plist

Replace all CRACKS files to default Dir.

Applications  /Applications/Native instruments/Battery
Plugins Dir (AU/VST/RTAS/)

OPEN FIRST STANDALONE VERSION!

Enjoy!
